{"dataType":"CVE_RECORD","dataVersion":"5.2","cveMetadata":{"cveId":"CVE-2024-6387","assignerOrgId":"53f830b8-0a3f-465b-8143-3b8a9948e749","state":"PUBLISHED","assignerShortName":"redhat","dateReserved":"2024-06-27T13:41:03.421Z","datePublished":"2024-07-01T12:37:25.431Z","dateUpdated":"2025-12-11T06:17:03.387Z"},"x_gcve":[{"vulnId":"GCVE-0-2024-6387","recordType":"advisory","relationships":[{"destId":"CVE-2024-6387","type":"equal"}],"x_vulnerability-lookup":{"url":"https://cve.circl.lu/vuln/CVE-2024-6387","source":"cve.circl.lu"}}],"x_range42":{"vuln":{"cve":["CVE-2024-6387"],"classifications":{"cwe":["CWE-364"],"owasp":null,"mitre_attack":["T1210"]},"product":"openssh","vendor":"OpenBSD","category":"network","title":"Openssh: regresshion - race condition in ssh allows rce/dos","url":"https://cve.circl.lu/vuln/CVE-2024-6387","cvss_score":8.1,"cvss_severity":"HIGH","cvss_vector":"CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:H/PR:N/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:H","exploitation":"poc","kev":null,"workarounds":["The below process can protect against a Remote Code Execution attack by disabling the LoginGraceTime parameter on Red Hat Enterprise Linux 9. However, the sshd server is still vulnerable to a Denial of Service if an attacker exhausts all the connections.\n\n1) As root user, open the /etc/ssh/sshd_config\n2) Add or edit the parameter configuration:\n~~~\nLoginGraceTime 0\n~~~\n3) Save and close the file\n4) Restart the sshd daemon:\n~~~\nsystemctl restart sshd.service\n~~~\n\nSetting LoginGraceTime to 0 disables the SSHD server's ability to drop connections if authentication is not completed within the specified timeout. If this mitigation is implemented, it is highly recommended to use a tool like 'fail2ban' alongside a firewall to monitor log files and manage connections appropriately.\n\nIf any of the mitigations mentioned above is used, please note that the removal of LoginGraceTime parameter from sshd_config is not automatic when the updated package is installed."],"solutions":null},"exercise":{"id":"r42-network-openssh-regresshion","version":"0.1.0","type":"docker","container":true,"difficulty":"advanced","stack":["openssh","glibc"],"estimated_time_minutes":null,"setup_cmd":"make up","teardown_cmd":"make down","poc_path":null},"catalog":{"path":"network/openssh/CVE-2024-6387","authors":["Benjamin Collas"],"license":"GPL-3.0-or-later","tags":["rce","race-condition","regresshion","ssh"],"status":"active"}}}
